  Source:
    Title: Young India
    Editor: M. K. Gandhi
    Locus:
      Date: 11 October 1928
---
I know that He, has no evil in Him and yet he there is evil, He is the author
of it and yet untouched by it. I know too that I shall never know God if
I do not wrestle with and against evil even at the cost of life itself.
